After a long discussion with Bridget, I realized I hate the media.

The media dictates what's cool. IE, if you don't have X brand of clothing or x whatever you're not considered "cool" and you're shunned. 

It dictates who can date who in a relationship.

It dictates what music is "good"

It controls our lives without us knowing it.

I hate the media.
